      "text": "Updat\n\nApplication Window \n(45 Days/105 for \nTransition) \n\nCustomer Engagement Window (60 Days/90 for Transition)\n\nPhase 1 Study (180 Days)\n\nPhase 2 Study (270 Days)\n\nNYISO Proposed Cluster Study Process Overview (Dec. 14, 2023 OC Mtg)\n\nPre Application Process Heatmap\n\nPre-Study\n\nApplication/ Site Control Submission $10,000 Application Fee ($5000 CRIS-only) Study Deposit (SD)\n\nPublish cluster member list w/in 10 BDs\n\nPhysical Infeasibility Screen Scoping Meeting\n\nDecision Period 1 (5 BDs)\n\nDecision Period 2 (10 BDs)\n\nIterative Final Decision Period\n\nIdentification \nand Cost \nEstimate of \nCTOAFs, Local \nSUFs, and \nDistribution \nUpgrade \nPre-Work for \nPhase 2 \nMIS/DIS \nAnalyses \nIdentification \nand Cost \nEstimate of \nSUFs and SDUs \n\nAdditional SDU Study and Iterative Decision Period As Applicable\n\nStudy Deposit (SD) Amounts\n\nRD1\n\nWP1\n\nor\n\nRD2\n\nWP2\n\nor\n\nSecurity\n\nWP3\n\nor\n\nReadiness Deposits (RD) /Security Amounts Withdrawal Penalty (WP) Amounts \nDeposit Amount \nRD1* $4,000/MW \nRD2* The greater of (i) RD1, and (ii) 20% \nof cost estimate determined in Phase \n1 for Local SUF and CTOAF \nSecurity 100% of cost estimate of SUFs, \nSDUs, and CTOAFs identified in \nPhase 1 and Phase 2 \n\nPenalty Amount WP1 25% of SD, except: (i) if interconnection physically infeasible, $5,000, or (ii) $0 if project withdraws within 5 BD of posting of cluster member list. WP2 50% of SD + 10% of RD1, except if interconnection physically infeasible, then only 25% of SD WP3 100% of SD +20% of RD2, except: (i) if interconnection physically infeasible then only 50% of SD, or (ii) if there is an increase of greater than 50% of total cost estimate between Phase 1 and Phase 2 (except SDU costs), then only 100% of SD\n\nSecurity Forfeiture\n\nUp to 100% of Security subject to forfeiture if other projects relying on the upgrades identified for its project\n\nSize Amount \n< 80 MW $100,000 \n≥ 80 < 200 \nMW \n\n$150,000 \n≥ 200 MW $250,000 \nCRIS Only $50,000 \n\nNegotiation of Interconnection and Construction Agreements\n\nLimited POI change w/in 5 BDs of list\n\nClustered study Clustered study\n\nNYISO Validation (5 BDs/10 for Transition) Address Deficiencies 10 BDs (15 for Transition) or end of Application Window\n\nSecurity Forfeiture\n\nUpdates to Phase 1 Analyses\n\n* N/A to CRIS only projects\n\nPost Phase 2 Study\n\n",
